properties.name: Size
properties.expression: const temp = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Lower in front').content('Offset Paths 1').amount * 2;[temp, temp]

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: function strokePath() {        // Limber Stroke        const thisProp = thisProperty;        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLin = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.scale[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p1').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p2ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p3ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const inTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.anchorPoint.value;            const outTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.position.value;            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p1').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p2ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p3ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,            ], [[0, 0], inTangPos, [0, 0]], [[0, 0], thisLayer.mul(outTangPos, -1), [0, 0]], false);        }    }strokePath();// Limber Library strokePath

properties.name: Size
properties.expression: const outlineWidth = thisLayer.effect('SpongeBob')('Outline Width');thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Inner').content('Sleeve End Group').content('Ellipse Path').size - [outlineWidth, outlineWidth]

properties.expression: const temp = Math.max(100 - thisLayer.effect('SpongeBob')('Rim Width'), (thisLayer.effect('SpongeBob')('Lower Width') / thisLayer.effect('SpongeBob')('Upper Width') * 100) + thisLayer.effect('SpongeBob')('Outline Width'));[temp, temp]

properties.name: Stroke Width
properties.expression: thisLayer.effect('SpongeBob')('Outline Width') * 2 * thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0] * 100 / (thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper in back').content('Stroke 1').strokeWidth * thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0])

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: const mywidth = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper in back').content('Stroke 1').strokeWidth;const rounding = thisLayer.effect('SpongeBob')('Rounding');const yScale = rounding == 0 ? 0.1 : rounding * 0.01 * mywidth;[mywidth,  yScale]

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('scaleFactor').transform.scale[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01;[scaleFactor * widthScale, 0]
